org.teamfarce.mirch.dialogue

Class SingleDialogueTreeAdder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.teamfarce.mirch.dialogue.SingleDialogueTreeAdder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDialogueTreeAdder

    public class SingleDialogueTreeAdder
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDialogueTreeAdder
    This represents a DialogueTreeAdder which adds the provided questionIntent to the provided dialogueTree when triggered.

    This class goes to an effort to make sure that the existence of this object does not cause the dialogueTree it is assosiated with to live on when it should not.
